scheduled_maintenances.name: [LIM1][Dedicated Servers] - Maintenance notification on multiple racks

incident_updates.body: As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Dedicated Servers infrastructure. Start time : 27/10/2025 04:00 UTC End time : 31/10/2025 16:00 UTC Service impact : From 29/10/2025 05:00 UTC to 29/10/2025 17:00 UTC, you may experience public network interruption on racks L101A11, L101A12, L101B11, L101B12 and L112B03 during this maintenance. Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy of our Dedicated Servers infrastructure, we will have to carry out interventions on the specified racks. Thank you for your understanding.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, we will be carrying out a maintenance on our cooling infrastructure. Start time : 27/10/2025 07:00 UTC End time : 27/10/2025 14:00 UTC Service impact : During this maintenance, the cooling system's efficiency may be temporarily reduced for some servers, potentially lowering performance. Despite ongoing mitigation efforts, customers could still experience a temporary reboot or shutdown in the worst case. Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy, we will be doing a maintenance on our cooling infrastructure. Thank you for your understanding.
